a major incursion from angola into namibia during the weekend 
said three western diplomats speaking on condition of anonymity 
the united states urged pretoria to exercise restraint 
washington also said it was holding urgent consultations with the 
soviet union cuba and angola to prevent the unraveling of the 
peace accord 
