taking advantage of the vacuum created because un peacekeepers 
still are deploying to monitor the peace agreement 
only about 1000 of the planned 4650 un troops have been 
deployed we have 300 men in the northern part of the area you 
cannot say it is a failure perez de cuellar said 
swapo south africa and angola said monday they remain committed 
to the un plan which calls for nov 1 elections leading to 
independence early next year 
