everyone said was born to be mayor 
on tuesday daley realized that destiny when he was elected to 
the office his father held for 21 years 
throughout a political career that had its beginnings nearly 30 
years ago the daley name made many of richard ms achievements 
possible diminished others and left him forever open to the 
